Package: roptgen
Type: Package
Title: Enhanced Option Accessors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "Ingerson", email = "smingerson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Sean Ingerson <smingerson@gmail.com>
Description: A toolkit for generating enhanced option accessors for packages or projects. Set 
    defaults, validate user-passed values against basic templates or function tests,
    and fail informatively. Code around options is frequently boilerplate, get past that and get to
    the rest of your project.
